{"pageProps":{"id":["posts","2014","common-commands-for-mysql"],"post":{"id":["posts","2014","common-commands-for-mysql"],"contentHtml":"<h2 id=\"hash-登陆mysql\">登陆mysql</h2>\n<div class=\"remark-highlight\"><pre class=\"language-unknown\"><code class=\"language-unknown\">mysql -u username -p</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"hash-创建用户名配置权限\">创建用户名配置权限</h2>\n<p>这里为该用户配置tablename表的全部权限，也可以指定</p>\n<div class=\"remark-highlight\"><pre class=\"language-unknown\"><code class=\"language-unknown\">GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON database.* TO &#x26;#39;username&#x26;#39;@&#x26;#39;hostname&#x26;#39; IDENTIFIED BY &#x26;#39;password&#x26;#39;;</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"hash-删除用户权限\">删除用户权限</h2>\n<p>使用revoke操作</p>\n<div class=\"remark-highlight\"><pre class=\"language-unknown\"><code class=\"language-unknown\">REVOKE ALL PRIVILEGES ON database.* FROM &#x26;#39;username&#x26;#39;@&#x26;#39;host&#x26;#39;;</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"hash-删除一个用户\">删除一个用户</h2>\n<div class=\"remark-highlight\"><pre class=\"language-unknown\"><code class=\"language-unknown\">DROP USER &#x26;amp;lsquo;username&#x26;#39;@&#x26;#39;host&#x26;#39;;</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"hash-修改用户密码\">修改用户密码</h2>\n<div class=\"remark-highlight\"><pre class=\"language-unknown\"><code class=\"language-unknown\">SET PASSWORD FOR &#x26;#39;username&#x26;#39; = PASSWORD(&#x26;#39;newpassword&#x26;#39;);</code></pre></div>\n","words":340,"toc":[{"depth":2,"value":"登陆mysql","id":"hash-登陆mysql"},{"depth":2,"value":"创建用户名配置权限","id":"hash-创建用户名配置权限"},{"depth":2,"value":"删除用户权限","id":"hash-删除用户权限"},{"depth":2,"value":"删除一个用户","id":"hash-删除一个用户"},{"depth":2,"value":"修改用户密码","id":"hash-修改用户密码"}],"title":"MySql 管理操作常用命令","author":"高国良","type":"posts","series":false,"date":"2014-07-10T01:44:00.791Z","tags":["mysql","password"],"description":"登录、权限、用户、密码","draft":false,"cover":false},"prev":{"title":"JS 事件调试 - 查找 HTML 元素绑定的事件以及绑定代码所在位置","author":"高国良","type":"posts","series":false,"date":1403780580791,"tags":["javascript","event","debug